# Project overview

**Repo:** `carlxaeron.github.io` · **Site:** [carlmanuel.com](https://carlmanuel.com) · **Version:** `package.json`

## Read first

- **History & current state:** [docs/project-history.md](../../docs/project-history.md)
- **Agent workflows:** [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md)

## Three subsystems

| Subsystem | Path | Deploy |
|-----------|------|--------|
| Portfolio V3 | `src/v3/` | GitHub Pages (`docs/`) |
| Firebase backend | `functions/` | `cd functions && npm run deploy` |
| Job applications | `OnlineJobs-MCP-Server/`, `job-applications/` | Local only |
| Client quotation sites | `client-sites/` | Netlify per folder · [catalog](client-sites/README.md) |

## Portfolio modes

- **Default:** 7-section slide deck (`home` … `quote`)
- **Preview:** `?preview=host.netlify.app` → device showcase (desktop 1280×800 + mobile 390×844 iframes, scaled to mockups)
- **Client demos:** embed-only on Netlify — direct URL blocked; view via portfolio preview only · [site catalog](client-sites/README.md)
- **Client stack:** Tailwind CDN + `site.js` interactivity (mobile nav, accordions, scroll reveal)
- **Outreach:** each `client-sites/{slug}/` includes draft email, SMS, and messenger quotations

`home` → `about` → `skills` → `experience` → `projects` → `contact` → `quote`

Config: `src/v3/containers/Portfolio/Portfolio.js` · Content: `src/external-config.js` · Preview: `src/v3/config/previewWhitelist.js`

